<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>James Lee</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700&family=Quicksand:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"> <!-- import Cinzel font cause it looks nice -->

    <script src="../script/script.js"></script> <!-- js script -->
</head>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<body>
    <div class="holo-bands"></div> <!-- create the background effect -->
    <nav class="navbar"> <div class="logo">James Lee</div>
        
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
            <li><a href="#blog">Blog</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
            <button class="theme-toggle">Dark Mode</button>
        </ul>

        <div class="hamburger">
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="mobile-menu">
        <button class="close-menu">&times;</button> <ul class="mobile-nav-links">
            <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
            <li><a href="#blog">Blog</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
            <button class="theme-toggle">Dark Mode</button>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="moon-glow"></div><div class="container">
            <h1>James' <span class="halo-text">Corner</span> of the World</h1>
            <p>I'm <span class="text-alt-ii">James</span>! I'll be posting about whatever I feel like, sharing about my life experiences and interesting things I learn. It doesn't hurt to look at life through rose-colored glasses, through an optimistic or romantic lens.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
        <div class="about-layout">
            <div class="about-text">
                <p>Hi! I'm a senior in high school. I'm planning on majoring in mathematics once I go to college, but plans may changeâ€”who knows what will happen?</p>
                <p>I have basic skills in <span class="text-alt-ii">Python</span>, <span class="text-alt-ii">Java</span>, and <span class="text-alt-ii">HTML/CSS</span>, but coding isn't something I'm dumping all my time into. I'm just trying to create something for fun.</p>
                <p>During a typical day, you can find me studying Japanese and Korean, playing table tennis, going on walks, and reading. I'm currently reading <span class="text-alt-ii">The Art of War</span> by Sun Tzu.</p>
                <p>Feel free to reach out or check out my blog!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="projects" class="container">
        <h2>Projects</h2>
        <div class="card-grid">
            <div class="card">
                <span class="card-meta">Card Meta</span>
                <h3>Project Name</h3>
                <p>This is a project description. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Nostrum, quia error cum deserunt explicabo iure ad velit.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn-link">View Case Study</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card">
                <span class="card-meta">App Development</span>
                <h3>Nebula Tracker</h3>
                <p>A productivity application that visualizes tasks as stars in a constellation.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn-link">View Case Study</a>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <span class="card-meta">UI Kit</span>
                <h3>Prism UI</h3>
                <p>An open-source React component library utilizing glassmorphism and light physics.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn-link">View Documentation</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="blog" class="container">
        <h2>James' Blog</h2>
        <div class="card-grid">
            <article class="card">
                <span class="card-meta">October 12, 2025</span>
                <h3>The Ethics of AI in Design</h3>
                <p>Exploring how artificial intelligence changes the creative process without losing the human touch.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn-link">Read Article</a>
            </article>

            <article class="card">
                <span class="card-meta">September 28, 2025</span>
