            <div class="socials">
                <a href="mailto:jleemails3000@gmail.com">Email</a>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/james-lee-4183b4297/">LinkedIn</a>
                <a href="https://github.com/Gask314">GitHub</a>
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/unorthodoxjames/">Instagram</a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--silver-accent);">
                &copy; 2026 James Lee / Built with "let's see what happens"
            </p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
